title: American Horror Story Freak Show - Interview with Ben Woolf
author: AHSPL
comment:
You know that moment when you watch a character in a show get hurt or die, and you search the actor who played that just so that you can remember that it's all pretend and he's okay in real life?

This is not one of those moments. RIP Ben Woolf.
I love his voice I could literally listen to him for hours
rest in paradise ben, always in our hearts
It's sad knowing how people treat such a great guy just because he's different. RIP Ben.
Us fans didn't know you, but I'm sure I can speak for all of us when I say you were too good for this world. You seemed so sweet and kind and pure
description: American Horror Story Freak Show - wywiad z Benem Woolfem.
